resources.description: It is currently a social issue for the institution of higher learning in our country to improve their education product quality. With an analysis of the professional features of computer network engineering major, we discuss a group of strategy factors related to the deployment of the major systemic reform in our university, including training objective, curriculum system, instructional resource, teaching method, practice education, content of course, teaching management, faculty and teaching evaluation. The factors discussed above are benefit of a draft process in order to launch a reform strategy for the computer network engineering major.
resources.name: Discussion on Factors of Reform Strategy Making for the Computer Network Engineering Major
